      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IF EVER (4) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by a neck at this track in a handy 26.11. Has a tricky draw to overcome but goes well over this trip. Has put together a string of wins and expected to go close again. DEALER (1) ran below best last time finishing fifth (26.61) over 461m at this track from Box 1. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. JUNGLE BOOGIE (2) is generally an honest type in the frame at 22 of 53 starts but missed the placings last time when fourth (26.14) over 461m at this track. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Has the ability and rates a key chance this line-up. KLONDIKE CLYDE (7) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
